{"statement":"To draw a line from a given point a line equal to a given line.\n","conclusion":"Thus, a line, AL, has been drawn from the given point A equal to the given line, BC.\n","steps":[{"text":"Let the given point be A and the given line BC.","reveal":["A","B","C","BC"]},{"text":"Join A and B. [p1]","reveal":["AB"]},{"text":"Draw an equilateral triangle, ADB, on AB. [1.1]","reveal":["AB","AD","BD","A","B","D"]},{"text":"Draw DA out to E [p2]","reveal":["DE","A","D"]},{"text":"Draw DB out to F [p2]","reveal":["DF","D","B"]},{"text":"Draw circle CGH with center B and radius BC, intersecting line DF at G. [p3]","reveal":["CGH","BC","B","C","G","H"]},{"text":"Draw circle GKL with center D and radius DG, intersecting line DE at L. [p3]","reveal":["GKL","G","K","L","D","DL"]},{"text":"Now BG will be equal to BC, since they are radii of circle CGH. [1d15]","reveal":["B","C","G","BG","BC","CGH"]},{"text":"DL will equal DG, since they are radii of of circle GKL.","reveal":["D","L","G","DL","DG","GKL"]},{"text":"DA was constructed equal to DB, so the remainders, AL and BG will be equal. [a3]","reveal":["A","L","B","G","AL","BG"]},{"text":"If AL is equal to BG, it must also be equal to BC, since BG equals BC. [a1]","reveal":["A","L","B","C","AL","BC"]}],"elements":[{"name":"A","type":"point","parents":[2,3]},{"name":"B","type":"point","parents":[3,4]},{"name":"C","type":"point","parents":[3,6]},{"name":"BC","type":"segment","parents":["B","C"]},{"name":"AB","type":"segment","parents":["A","B"]},{"name":"CIR1","type":"circle","parents":["A","B"]},{"name":"CIR2","type":"circle","parents":["B","A"]},{"name":"D","type":"intersection","parents":["CIR1","CIR2"]},{"name":"AD","type":"segment","parents":["A","D"]},{"name":"BD","type":"segment","parents":["B","D"]},{"name":"CGH","type":"circle","parents":["B","C"]},{"name":"H","type":"glider","parents":["CGH"]},{"props":{"straightLast":true,"straightFirst":false},"name":"DF","type":"line","parents":["D","B"]},{"name":"G","type":"intersection","parents":["CGH","DF"]},{"props":{"straightLast":true,"straightFirst":false},"name":"DE","type":"line","parents":["D","A"]},{"name":"GKL","type":"circle","parents":["D","G"]},{"name":"K","type":"glider","parents":["GKL"]},{"name":"L","type":"intersection","parents":["GKL","DE"]},{"name":"DL","type":"segment","parents":["D","L"]},{"name":"BG","type":"segment","parents":["B","G"]},{"name":"DG","type":"segment","parents":["D","G"]},{"name":"AL","type":"segment","parents":["A","L"]}]}
